OL,3,CMan in court accused of fatally
OL,4,Cstabbing 77-year-old in front of
OL,5,Cmarket shoppers
OL,7,FA 66-year-old man has appeared in
OL,8,Fcourt accused of stabbing to death a
OL,9,Fman in front of shoppers at a historic
OL,10,FSunday market.
OL,12,FMusse Ali is also accused of attacking
OL,13,Ftwo other men during the knife attack
OL,14,Fat East Street Market in Walworth,
OL,15,Fsouth London.
