OL,3,CMan in court accused of fatally
OL,4,Cstabbing 77-year-old in front of
OL,5,Cmarket shoppers
OL,7,FAli, of no fixed address, spoke only
OL,8,Fto confirm his name and address via a
OL,9,FSomalian interpreter, as he appeared
OL,10,Fat Croydon Magistrates' Court on
OL,11,FTuesday to face charges of one count
OL,12,Fof murder, two counts of attempted
OL,13,Fmurder and one of knife possession.
OL,15,FHilkiah McLeggan, 77, from Southwark,
OL,16,Fsouth London, was pronounced dead at
OL,17,Fthe scene.
OL,19,FTwo others are seriously injured in
OL,20,Fhospital, one in a critical condition.
