OL,3,CMan in court accused of fatally
OL,4,Cstabbing 77-year-old in front of
OL,5,Cmarket shoppers
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police has said it
OL,8,Fwas not a terrorist attack and urged
OL,9,Fthe public not to speculate on any
OL,10,Fpotential motive.
OL,12,FThe force has thanked "brave members
OL,13,Fof the public who assisted police at
OL,14,Fthe scene" amid reports that traders
OL,15,Ftackled and held the suspected
OL,16,Fknifeman until officers arrived.
