OL,3,CMan in court accused of fatally
OL,4,Cstabbing 77-year-old in front of
OL,5,Cmarket shoppers
OL,7,FChief Superintendent Seb Adjei-Addoh,
OL,8,Flead for policing in Southwark, said:
OL,9,F"There will be an increased policing
OL,10,Fpresence in the Walworth area as we
OL,11,Fwork alongside our partners to provide
OL,12,Freassurance to local people and small
OL,13,Fbusinesses operating in East Street."
OL,15,FDistrict Judge Nigel McLean told Ali,
OL,16,Fwho wore a grey tracksuit as he stood
OL,17,Fin the dock: "The charges you face are
OL,18,Fmatters that can only be tried in
OL,19,Fcrown court in the main.
