OL,7,F"My only function today is to formally
OL,8,Fsend you to the Central Criminal Court
OL,9,Fwhere your trial will take place."
OL,11,FAli was remanded in custody to appear
OL,12,Fat the Old Bailey on Wednesday for his
OL,13,Fbail to be determined and on December
OL,14,F10 for a plea hearing.
